                I finished this book because it got a tremendous applaud on douban. A lot of people say that it is a book which describes normal Chinese with deep understanding and observation. This book is a story about an american younger who cross the long distance between China and US as a volunteer teacher. He taught English to village high school students in FuLin, a long-history traditional chinese city in southwest china. And in this situation, he melt his thinking and observation with his all passion to became a writer into a useful research about Chinese emotion and custom. 
